locality: Small river valley leading into the Sakamena River, c. 4 km SE of Parcelle 1, Beza Mahafaly Reserve. In damp sandy banks amongst grasses in the river bed.
District: Morombe, Commune: Tanandava Angarazy, Fokontany: Tanandava Angarazy. Dans une plantation de riz. Sur sol argilo-sableux. Échantillon préservé en alcool.
Harerge: 30 km SE of Kebri Dehar, Banka Qorraxay
4.6km by road towards Forsayth from Georgetown.
